      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Leo and Jordan are chilled though. We wait in the lines, have cute conversations and sail through the whole process pretty painlessly. There’s a chance we won’t get it in time, but we’ve done out best. We’re throwing up the idea of not going for the Schengen visa and rather doing a longer motorbike trip through turkey and maybe Albania. This sounds good. ",
            "link": null
