            "content": "On the way out of the building Jordan almost has a heart attack when Petit Noir is in the lift with us. We chat about it for a while afterwards. Hunger is calling and Jordan has an hour before her conference and Vida is close and convenient. They make a damn good chorizo toasted cheese. ",
