            "content": "It’s a Monkey Gin promotion night and I choose a burnt pineapple, soda and gin cocktail - delicious. Jordan goes for a negroni which is powerful and great. A charming promotion man comes up to us with all the moves and charisma. He makes me spin a wheel as I have ordered a Money gin cocktail, I come away with a free ticket to another gin cocktail. ",
